    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 2 Creation Points </p><p>Keyword: Weapon </p><p>Drain: 5 CCD Chakra </p><p></p><p>A large katana-like blade made industrialized steel.</p><p> It is a Melee Blade Weapon with a Reach of 10ft and deals: 1d8 + Dex in slashing damage on a hit.</p><p> On your turn, you can spend the CCD Drain and send an arc of electricity through the blade.</p><p> Until the end of your next turn, the Ion Sword's damage die increases by 1 step and deals lightning damage.</p><p> It also gains +1 to attack and damage rolls.</p><p></p>",
